{"tid":118040,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"（扶桑水果）熊本露之水滴士多啤梨 睌白柚 車厘茄 加博多甜王士多啤梨食評","createTime":"2017-02-12T16:52:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-16T16:41:57.000Z","uid":21545,"like":11,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d8d54c4b17c0f98ebef06dbf3db84985b1233f62","tid":118040,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T16:52:27.000Z","msg":"琴日 同女女去行sogo 遇上百年難得一遇既 扶桑美食節<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一埸嘴巴既美夢 荷包既惡夢 即將開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n價錢 <br />\n露之水滴 士多啤梨 $192 兩盒 十幾粒<br />\n晚白柚 $179<br />\n車厘茄 $28 十粒<br />\n甜王士多啤梨 $69<br />\n<br />\n熊本士多啤梨 味道酸酸甜甜 帶有濃烈既士多啤梨香 肉質軟而不爛<br />\n食完之後士多啤梨既香味會在囗腔中迴盪住 久久不散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1e0Yy9G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1e0Yy9G.jpg&h=ccf7bedd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/13/003720_1b5178461261a8d703c391122c4ddfbc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F13%2F003720_1b5178461261a8d703c391122c4ddfbc.jpg&h=f00cd49d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n晚白柚 味道 入口極酸 但不苦不澀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲帶有陣陣柚既清香 果肉粒粒飽滿多汁 簡直係柚中一絕 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dcf12zd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDcf12zd.jpg&h=cd339299&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔記得影 得番個襟章<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n熊本車厘茄 味道微酸 帶鹹味 入口會爆漿 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  入面既茄汁滲住絲絲既蕃茄香 抵佢賣咁貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/13/004748_e26d244901b2722bc642d3e00e599fff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F13%2F004748_e26d244901b2722bc642d3e00e599fff.jpg&h=3a6c5dec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n甜王士多啤梨 味道重甜重酸 肉質過軟 整體還可以 但較露之水滴遜色<br />\n冇圖 唔記得影 sor <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總括 扶桑水果 好貴 但物超所值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4051b60da9a5bc7c072a25ceca6722d5edcaeb9a","tid":118040,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T17:00:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7358d42cda5742b6f5c3e8d473837896fb9833a9","tid":118040,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T17:12:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0833c6f9927e209074d610341f369e5e5292bfaa","tid":118040,"uid":21488,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T17:15:39.000Z","msg":"你快撚d同d南亞狗死開12邊啦"},{"pid":"b8ae869f56f3413743f6d81640d2cba1